The paper discusses an online gradient descent algorithm for large scale machine learning problems. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
